19 9–275.
20 (A) (1) IN THIS SECTION THE FOLLOWING WORDS HAVE THE MEANINGS
21 INDICATED.
22 (2) “DISCOUNT STORE” MEANS A RETAIL STORE THAT OFFERS FOR
